 Lisa Mangena, Court Reporter A BULAWAYO police officer was allegedly rushed to hospital clutching his manhood after his wife assaulted him for “stealing her clothes.” Melody Mpofu (38) of Mpopoma suburb allegedly hit Mr Cannan Phiri (45) once on the testicles. The couple fought after Mpofu allegedly took $480 from Mr Phiri’s wallet, which she said she would use to replace the stolen clothes.